23
00:02:53,666 --> 00:02:55,833
Rufus Lore!

24
00:02:56,750 --> 00:03:00,416
[CHAPATI]
From Lamia Scale, Lyon Bastia!

25
00:03:01,750 --> 00:03:06,166
[CHAPATI] From Fairy Tail
Team A, the icy Gray Fullbuster!

26
00:03:07,250 --> 00:03:11,416
[CHAPATI] From Fairy
