moment of Hidden!

32
00:03:23,250 --> 00:03:25,791
[HAPPY] Night of Shooting Stars!

33
00:03:26,791 --> 00:03:28,375
It's time for the
Grand Magic Games,

34
00:03:28,458 --> 00:03:30,166
and I couldn't be more excited!

35
00:03:30,250 --> 00:03:31,375
Allow me to go
over the rules just

36
00:03:31,458 --> 00:03:34,375
one more time,
so no one gets confused!

37
00:03:34,458 --> 00:03:36,875
[MAVIS] Each team is made up
of five members at the most.

38
00:03:37,375 --> 00:03:39,041
But according
to what Porlyusica

39
00:03:39,125 --> 00:03:41,291
said about the
situation with Wendy.

40
00:03:42,583 --> 00:03:45,416
[PORLYUSICA]
No need for water-works, child.

41
00:03:45,500 --> 00:03:48,708
I'm sure you'll get to
participate, once you're well.

42
00:03:50,291 --> 00:03:51,458
And make no mistake,

43
00:03:51,541 --> 00:03:53,958
you will recover
now that I'm here.

44
00:03:54,041 --> 00:03:56,208
On my honor as a healer.

45
00:03:56,833 --> 00:03:57,958
The organizers
do allow reserve

46
