members for when
something happens.

47
00:04:00,250 --> 00:04:03,291
Poor little Wendy was attacked
by those meanies in Raven Tail.

48
00:04:03,375 --> 00:04:04,625
But hopefully she'll
still get a chance

49
00:04:04,708 --> 00:04:06,166
to take part in the games!

50
00:04:06,583 --> 00:04:08,416
[MAVIS] Eight teams
made it past the qualifying

51
00:04:08,500 --> 00:04:10,583
round to move on
to the main competition.

52
00:04:10,666 --> 00:04:13,125
Including two different
teams from Fairy Tail!

53
00:04:13,458 --> 00:04:14,791
I'm so proud!

54
00:04:16,416 --> 00:04:18,000
Those are the only teams I care
about, so I'll skip the others.

55
00:04:18,083 --> 00:04:19,541
[JET AND DROY] You can
do whatever you want!

56
00:04:19,625 --> 00:04:20,708
[MAVIS]
The whole tournament will

57
00:04:20,791 --> 00:04:22,916
take place over the
course of five days.

58
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:25,291
Why don't we take a
closer look at the schedule?

59
00:04:25,375 --> 00:04:27,291
Each day is divided
into two parts:

60
00:04:27,375 --> 00:04:29,583
