followed by a battle.

61
00:04:29,666 --> 00:04:30,833
The teams can
choose any member

62
00:04:30,916 --> 00:04:33,000
they want to participate
in the first part.

63
00:04:33,083 --> 00:04:36,208
And this here will tell us how
the scores are calculated.

64
00:04:36,958 --> 00:04:38,583
[MAVIS] But, for
the battles, it's the

65
00:04:38,666 --> 00:04:41,166
organizers who choose
the participants!

66
